## List.type property

Type of list.

LIST is vertical, translates to a List on Google and ListTemplate1 on Alexa CAROUSEL is horizontal, translates to a Carousel on Google and ListTemplate2 on Alexa

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
type: "LIST" | "CAROUSEL";
```
